<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="neighbourhood-n">neighbo(u)rhood <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'neɪbəhʊd/    美 /'neɪbərhʊd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 社区；街坊；(某特定的) 地段：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I live in a quiet neighbourhood. 
我居住的社区很安静。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The houses in that neighbourhood are expensive. 
那个地段的房子很贵。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-the-neighbourhood">2.★ <strong>[集体名词，用the neighbourhood，谓语动词用单数] 附近地区 (的居民)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>All the neighbourhood</strong> is aware of it. 
所有邻居都知道这件事。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I want to live <strong>in the neighbourhood of</strong> my office. 
我想住在公司附近。</p></div></div>